name: The Decemberists
text: But what about merch, you ask? If you‚Äôre replicating the in-concert experience down to the sticky, beer-stained floors, where‚Äôs the merch? O, have no fear: we have t-shirts and prints available to bundle with your tickets as well.

name: The Decemberists
text: VIP packages will be available for the shows as well, which you can imagine as a sort of post-show hangout ‚Äî through our screens. You‚Äôll be able to ask the band your burning questions AND be privy to three extra songs we‚Äôll have performed just for you.

name: The Decemberists
text: Announcing: TWENTY (OR TWENTY ONE) YEARS BEFORE THE MAST: THE INTERNET CONCERTS!  Three special shows, each with their own unique setlist that span our entire career, happening on April 11, 18, 25. Tickets for individual shows and bundles available now. https://t.co/m0NeIbZMGp https://t.co/0s85a9sd77

name: The Decemberists
text: In the meantime, we‚Äôre putting together a different kind of anniversary celebration, and we‚Äôll be in touch on that soon.

name: The Decemberists
text: We plan on touring next summer; whether that will be in the vein of a similar tour or something new altogether, it‚Äôs too soon to say. We promise to be out there again, seeing all your shining, singing faces ‚Äî covered or uncovered.

name: The Decemberists
text:
There‚Äôs so much uncertainty about playing these shows safely, especially the indoor ones, that we thought the best decision is to cancel. Yeah, we‚Äôre bummed.

Refunds are available now at point of purchase.

name: The Decemberists
text: We were really hoping to be able to bring this 20th/21st anniversary show on the road this summer. And while there‚Äôs every reason to be optimistic about the state of the pandemic and the possibility of live shows in the future, we don‚Äôt think it‚Äôs going to happen in July/August.
